  "keyFeatures": [
    "Instant on-demand CSS generation — no parsing, no AST scanning, 5x faster than alternatives",
    "Fully customizable preset system — all utilities are provided via composable presets",
    "Pure CSS icons via @unocss/preset-icons supporting any Iconify icon set",
    "Attributify mode to group utilities in HTML attributes",
    "Transformers for variant groups, CSS directives (@apply), and compile-class optimization",
